#BreakingNews @ #Coronavirus #vaccination 

The Centre on Friday said that it is gearing up to roll-out a #COVID19 #vaccine in #India and will conduct a two-day "DRY RUN" in four states (#AndhraPradesh, #Assam, #Gujarat, #Punjab) on December 28-29 to check their preparedness. https://t.co/nqUuCAsyPt
